headline: Protiviti Congratulates Brand Ambassador James Nicholas on Victory at the Astara Golf Championship presented by Mastercard
summary: Protiviti golf brand ambassador and professional golfer James Nicholas secured the first win of his career at the Astara Golf Championship presented by Mastercard in Bogota, Colombia. Nicholas completed rounds of 68-65-66-66 (-19).
